sentences: Mounir grew up in Tunis, and he received his diploma  Arabic music in 1998.
He made his debut with Fadhel Jaziri and his show Hadhra in 1994, and in the early 2000s he formed Nagouz.
In 2010 he released his album Tawassol.
Mounir announced Bach on the bac' as his next project in June 2018.
